    • calcTotals

      public void calcTotals(DateTransactionCurrencypairMap dateTransactionCurrencypairMap)
      Calculates and aggregates totals from all individual account position summaries within this group. Applies current exchange rates for foreign currency conversions and updates all group totals.
      Parameters:
      dateTransactionCurrencypairMap - currency exchange rate context for FX calculations
